Description:
Anatomy and physiology - Introduction to the structure and function of the body
Anatomy & Physiology - start step by step with a visual introduction to each system of the human body. This app uses 3D models, illustrations and 3D animations to present the core concepts for beginners and knowledgeable. For you tried a group of highly qualified specialists, whose work was checked by doctors and anatomists. So everything in its place and the error is excluded.

Put aside the textbook, lab samples or plastic 3D model and immerse yourself in breathtaking 3D experience. Visible Body creates innovative, interactive 3D human anatomy and physiology content and applications. If you love the human body, you will love Visible Body! Doctors of Sciences, professors, nurses and students are among the people who use the application developed by Visible Body in order to make learning and teaching anatomy and physiology visual and engaging
